<ul><li> It turns out that Saber had her own Sexy Mentor in the form Merlin, whose <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/Bishounen" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/Bishounen">appearance</a> and <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/LovableSexManiac" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/LovableSexManiac">personality</a> more obviously reflect his <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/HornyDevils" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/HornyDevils">incubus</a> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/HalfHumanHybrid" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/HalfHumanHybrid">heritage</a> than do most depictions. <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/AllThereInTheManual" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/AllThereInTheManual">Grand Order Character Materials</a> describes him as the sexy version of Gandalf.
<div class="indent"><em>Make way for the Middle Earth Prettyboy!</em>
</div></li></ul></li><li> <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VisualNovel/TheLabyrinthOfGrisaia" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VisualNovel/TheLabyrinthOfGrisaia">The Labyrinth of Grisaia</a></em>: Yuuji's master, Asako Kusakabe had sex with him on his birthday. She encouraged him to sleep with her best friend as well. However, Asako was Yuuji's <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/FirstLove" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/FirstLove">First Love</a> and he was heartbroken when she passed away.
</li><li> <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VisualNovel/MyVowToMyLiege" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VisualNovel/MyVowToMyLiege">My Vow To My Liege</a></em>: The protagonist <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/SweetPollyOliver" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/SweetPollyOliver">Fuchai</a> can choose to romance her mentor <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/SilverFox" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/SilverFox">Wu Zixu</a>, who has a bad habit of pulling a <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/MentorOccupationalHazard" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/MentorOccupationalHazard">mentor sacrifice</a> in other routes.
